title: Fox MX Presents | Taddy's Championship Weekend
description:
Fox team rider Taddy Blazusiak captures his fifth consecutive AMA Endurocross Championship. See the action that went down at the final round in Las Vegas. 

Music:
Artist: Mochipet 
Song: The Battle Of Dinopolis 
Album Title: Chicxclub
